name: Harry Garrett
description: I’m a down to earth person who likes to enjoy life – and who is outgoing,Practical, Responsible, Sensitive, Patient I love to have a good conversation, and to laugh out loud. I am romantic and would like to share my life with the right woman. I’m looking for somebody who is romantic, loves live, happy, caring, very sensual, and beautiful woman on the inside. Somebody who is my best friend and we can move in the same direction together.
